com.tinkerpop.blueprints.util.wrappers

Class WrapperVertexQuery

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tinkerpop.blueprints.util.wrappers.WrapperVertexQuery
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Query, VertexQuery

    public abstract class WrapperVertexQuery
extends Object
implements VertexQuery
    A WrapperQuery is useful for wrapping the construction and results of a Vertex.query(). Any necessary Iterable wrapping must occur when Vertex.vertices() or Vertex.edges() is called.
    Author:
    Marko A. Rodriguez (http://markorodriguez.com)
